      <scopecontent id="aspace_955161a0877c766b879f4cc4e3660ae9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs documenting Viola Barnes's (Yale 1919 PhD) student life at Yale and in New Haven. Included are photographs of fellow women graduate students, friends, outings, and activities.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
